    <item>
      <title>特朗普宣布互惠关税时，商品影响混合</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-02/commodities-impact-mixed-as-trump-announces-reciprocal-tariffs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）总统宣布的漫长的宣布对向美国进口的互惠关税揭幕，引发了石油价格下跌，而黄金上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-02/commodities-impact-mixed-as-trump-announces-reciprocal-tariffs</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 02 Apr 2025 22:40:33 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>亚洲资产看到的较高的美国关税遭受了重击</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-02/asian-assets-seen-taking-a-pounding-from-higher-us-tariffs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据战略家称，亚洲经济体首当其冲，唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）的关税洪水泛滥，其货币和股票预计将承受销售压力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-02/asian-assets-seen-taking-a-pounding-from-higher-us-tariffs</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 02 Apr 2025 22:39:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>当特朗普颠覆全球交易订单时，美国股票期货跌跌撞撞</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-02/s-p-500-futures-tumble-as-trump-upends-global-trading-order</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在唐纳德·特朗普总统概述了美国交易的一系列关税之后，美国股票期货暴跌了3％以上，这增加了一场成熟的贸易战争的可能性，这可能使美国经济陷入衰退。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-02/s-p-500-futures-tumble-as-trump-upends-global-trading-order</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 02 Apr 2025 22:03:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>华尔街游戏超出了特朗普的关税对世界市场的意义</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-02/wall-street-game-plans-what-trump-tariffs-mean-for-world-markets</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）对他在“解放日”的高潮时破坏现代交易秩序的威胁使他的威胁变得良好之后，华尔街交易者被拖延。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-02/wall-street-game-plans-what-trump-tariffs-mean-for-world-markets</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 02 Apr 2025 21:49:10 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国不包括钢，铝，黄金来自相互关税</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-02/us-excludes-steel-aluminum-copper-gold-from-reciprocal-tariff</link>
      <description><![CDATA[白宫说，钢铁和铝进口商品将不受互惠关税的限制，这将至少为已经征收25％责任的国内买家提供一些救济，从汽车到洗碗机的所有主要金属的所有进口。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-02/us-excludes-steel-aluminum-copper-gold-from-reciprocal-tariff</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 02 Apr 2025 21:43:02 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>随着紧张局势的增加，中国限制了公司对美国进行投资</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-02/china-restricts-companies-from-investing-in-us-as-tensions-rise</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据熟悉此事的人们说，中国已采取措施限制当地公司对美国的投资，这可能使北京与特朗普政府有关潜在的贸易谈判有更多的杠杆作用。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-02/china-restricts-companies-from-investing-in-us-as-tensions-rise</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 02 Apr 2025 10:02:28 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
